---
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-tag"><div class="dot"></div>Disponible · Junior Developer</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">
      <span class="line1">Hola, soy</span>
      <span class="line2">Sebastian.</span>
    </h1>
